{"tid":1226784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習種生日，做乜個蛋糕咁大整估","createTime":"2019-06-15T13:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:56:59.000Z","uid":20563,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b7910a78eebaf765e0e06e85fa304faa75b38c","tid":1226784,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"在塔吉克出席「亞洲相互協作與信任措施會議」第五次峰會的俄羅斯總統普京，前往國家主席習近平入住的酒店，祝賀他66歲生日。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯傳媒報道，普京向習近平贈送俄羅斯雪糕，習近平回贈中國茶葉。<br />\n<br />\n普京高度評價習近平在俄中關係發展中發揮的重要作用，強調不久前習近平對俄羅斯國事訪問取得圓滿成功，相信俄中關係將繼續保持良好發展勢頭。習近平對普京表示感謝，指出普京在中國很受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463045-20190615.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463045-20190615.htm&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=55b8b22e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463045-20190615.htm&h=df918dc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463045-20190615.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n個蛋糕 66大順 寫到 666 順<br />\n今次真係要唱 hallelujah <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJSi6G9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJSi6G9.png&h=2ac68cb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8945e9e8704b927df91c687f6b322cea0a0d2311","tid":1226784,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:22:14.000Z","msg":"666 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8fe1a7c01225ea52c953e55e1b65de56323abf","tid":1226784,"uid":50196,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"以為寫住平反六四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546a291991102486467b7225e4b05585333624a9","tid":1226784,"uid":171192,"like"